@page "/system"
@attribute [Authorize]
@layout PlatformLayout

<PageTitle>Platform System</PageTitle>

<section class="panel">
    <p class="eyebrow">System</p>
    <h1>Platform host bootstrap status</h1>
    <p>
        The dedicated platform apphost is now running as a separate client and server pair so control-plane
        administration can evolve without leaking back into the tenant host.
    </p>
</section>

<section class="grid">
    <article class="panel">
        <h2>Platform endpoints</h2>
        <ul>
            <li>`/` platform home</li>
            <li>`/platform-admin` control-plane administration</li>
            <li>`/api/system/info` platform host metadata</li>
            <li>`/health` platform host health checks</li>
        </ul>
    </article>

    <article class="panel">
        <h2>Current migration focus</h2>
        <ul>
            <li>Move remaining platform-only flows off the tenant host.</li>
            <li>Keep RPC/contracts shared while host shells stay separated.</li>
            <li>Clean tenant routing back down to tenant-only concerns.</li>
        </ul>
    </article>
</section>
